TierLevelForecastParams.description:
Forecast params with optional tier-specific overrides.

Inherits all global what-if params from ForecastParams.
When tier-specific params are provided, they calculate contributions
to global metrics from each performance tier.

Performance tiers (based on ACOS):
- good: ACOS < 30%
- mid: 30% <= ACOS <= 40%
- poor: ACOS > 40%
- no_sales: sales = 0

Example request body:
{
    "ad_spend_what_if": 5,       // Global: increase ad spend by 5%
    "good": {
        "ad_spend_what_if": 10   // Good tier: increase ad spend by 10%
    },
    "poor": {
        "ad_spend_what_if": -20  // Poor tier: decrease ad spend by 20%
    }
}
